<Author>kkm_8
<Content>Great Experience I am a single female, who travels worldwide weekly for business and several times a year for vacations. I write very few reviews. The Mandala Suites deserves a great review. I was fortunate enough to stay in 2 different rooms the same trip (my flights were cancelled due to a hurricane at home and they helped to accomodate my extra day). Below are my quick impressions.1. Very Clean (I'm in Medical  can be very germ phobic; this is very important to me)2. 1st room on 7th floor was 800sq ft. open and very comfortable.3. Cleaning staff was quick, courteous and reliable4. Front desk staff was VERY accomodating/helpful and always cheerful 5. Rooms were quiet and well supplied6. Showers for a Europe hotel (not always what an American expects) were clean, large, and had plenty of really hot water7. Great location for shopping, the convention center, restaurants and tours. In total, A Great place to stay and I hope there staff receives many compliments! 
