<Author>Great_Dane_Dillema
<Content>Great suite, great price, great stay Our stay was excellent. The staff were very polite, friendly, helpful and welcoming. The suite itself was extremely comfortable, as well as being very secure. The kitchen area was perfect, and had plenty of utensils and tableware. The room was very clean and kept clean throughout our stay.The only area that we were disappointed with was that the linen was not changed during our 5 night stay. I would have expected one change of towels during our stay and that the shower gel and shampoo bottles would have been restocked once used.Other than that, the suite made our stay in Berlin a very enjoyable experience. It was wonderful to have such a large and welcoming space to retire to, after a long day of sightseeing and shopping! I will definitely be recommending the Mandala Suites to anybody who intends to travel to Berlin. For the money, I just can't see how this place could be beat. If you're after the complete hotel experience however i.e. room service etc, stay elsewhere. 
