<Content>Great Hotel The Mandala is superbly situated, right in the centre of Berlin with access to two subway lines within a block. The hotel is exceptionally quiet, especially if you have a room on the court. The rooms are spacious and exceptionally clean and having cooking facilities is great for longer stays. The staff is very helpful. The breakfast is superb, if pricey at 17Euros. The hotel doesn't have a restaurant but there is a very good Bavarian restaurant in the complex where the food is very good, copious, and reasonable. 
